  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and sauté until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the cannellini beans, soya milk, fermented vegetable juice, and rice vinegar.",
    "Stir well to combine and bring to a simmer.",
    "Add the Arborio rice and stir to coat with the liquid.",
    "If using white wine, add it now and stir to deglaze the pan.",
    "Reduce heat to low and cook, stirring occasionally, for 20-25 minutes or until the rice is cooked and the liquid has been absorbed.",
    "Stir in the grated Parmesan cheese and season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh parsley."
  ],
